{"data":{"items":[{"content":"{\"images\":[],\"audios\":[],\"imageTotalCount\":0,\"audioTotalCount\":0,\"text\":\"如果手指发力为主，则不容易进入放松的状态。\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2022-10-29T00:54:20+0800","evaluateStatus":1,"id":11891197,"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20220602/2022060208442182070043.jpg","ccUserName":"jnukant001","identity":1,"nickName":"一定写好字吖","userId":151885219},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"text\":\"手指的受力是大致有如此的差异，不过需要注意的是，整体发力是手臂手腕手指共同参与，手腕发力为主，并非手指发力为主，若是手指发力为主则会造成手疼痛。这个需要注意。 控笔功夫的增长需要时间，等到控笔功夫纯熟之后，以手臂手腕带动行笔，才能更自然地进入心流的状态。 \",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2022-10-29T00:53:14+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":11891194,"parentUserInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20231028/2023102801220220683569.jpg","ccUserName":"宅小星","identity":0,"nickName":"小星星","userId":13649940},"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20220602/2022060208442182070043.jpg","ccUserName":"jnukant001","identity":1,"nickName":"一定写好字吖","userId":151885219},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"text\":\"今日感悟：写横线主要是用拇指发力去“推”笔杆，写竖线主要用中指往下“抵”笔杆。今晚太困了，明早起来接着练。\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2022-10-29T00:02:16+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":11891064,"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20231028/2023102801220220683569.jpg","ccUserName":"宅小星","identity":0,"nickName":"小星星","userId":13649940},"userPower":0}],"nextPage":false},"message":"success","status":0}